Context:
Career Services provides support for students and alumni through virtual and in-person means. They offer resources for hiring and supporting diversity and accessibility in the workplace. Interested individuals can email careerservices@georgebrown.ca or visit one of their locations. The contact numbers are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559, and they can be reached at ask.george@georgebrown.ca. Their social media hub is also available for visits. They have a Student Employment Guide with eligibility information and a land acknowledgment to learn about. Users can sign up to receive updates on application deadlines, college news, events, tours, and more. The information in the website is subject to change without notice.
